org.colomoto.logicalmodel.io

Interface LogicalModelFormat

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFormat, GINMLFormat, SBMLFormat

    public interface LogicalModelFormat
    Description of an available file format. Implement this interface to integrate new formats in the conversion tool.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi
